resources.description:
> ### This method updates a secretary registered in the database.

> **PUT** _/secretario/:id

- **Request**


  > - Note: **You can update secretary information/data.**
  > - Type: ***application/json***
  > - Body: 
        {
              "nomeCompleto": string,
              "cpf": string,
              "email": string,
              "senhaAcesso": string, 
              "matricula": string,
              "telefone": [string],
              "endereco": [string],
              "data de nascimento": [string]
        }
       
  
  
  - **Response**
 
  
>     
    "message": string,
                {
                "Secretário atualizado com sucesso.": successful,
                }
     "item": data
             {
             "nomeCompleto": string,
             "cpf": string,
             "dataNascimento": [string],
             "email": string,
             "telefone": [string],
             "endereco": [string],
             "senhaAcesso": string, 
             "matricula": string
             }
      "error":{
          "message": string,
                {
                "Falha na requisição": failure,
                }
      }

resources.name: Cadastrar Secretário
resources.description:
> ### This method register a secretary in the database.

> **POST** _secretario/

- **Request**

  > - Note: **You can register secretary, sending the desired data in the request body.**
  > - Type: ***application/json***
  > - Body: 
        {
             required "nomeCompleto": string,
             required "cpf": string,
             required "email": string,
             required "senhaAcesso": string, 
             required "matricula": string,
                      "telefone": [string],
                      "endereco": [string],
                      "data de nascimento": [string]
        }
       
       
   - **Response**
 
  > - Note: **Examples of success and failure messages.**
  
>     
    "data": {
    "message": string,
                     {
                     "Secretário cadastrado com sucesso.": successful,
                     "Falha na requisição.": failure,
                     }
    "item": {
             "nomeCompleto": string,
             "cpf": string,
             "email": string,
             "senhaAcesso": string, 
             "matricula": string,
             "telefone": [string],
             "endereco": [string],
             "data de nascimento": [string]
            }
            }
